---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="联系AILD" description="联系AILD获取AI领导力与发展咨询支持。" canonical="https://aild.org/zh/contact/" active="contact" lang="zh-CN">
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">联系我们</p>
    <h1>预约AI领导力咨询</h1>
    <p class="lead">请发送团队规模、关键决策场景和目标结果，我们会给出30天执行路径。</p>
    <div class="stack">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact-form">提交咨询表单</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/zh/templates/">先看模板</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section panel">
    <h2>建议填写这些信息</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>团队规模与主要职能</li>
      <li>当前最想改善的关键决策场景</li>
      <li>数据、合规、工具等现实约束</li>
      <li>未来30到90天希望达成的结果</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section panel">
    <h2>提交咨询</h2>
    <p>请填写下面表单，信息会直接发送到我们的邮箱。</p>
    <form
      id="contact-form"
      name="aild-contact-zh"
      method="POST"
      action="https://formsubmit.co/chenchen2012@hotmail.com"
      class="contact-form"
    >
      <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://aild.org/zh/contact-success/" />
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="AILD 中文咨询" />
      <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
      <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table" />
      <input type="text" name="_honey" class="hidden-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

      <label>
        姓名
        <input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="name" required />
      </label>
      <label>
        邮箱
        <input type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required />
      </label>
      <label>
        团队或机构
        <input type="text" name="organization" autocomplete="organization" />
      </label>
      <label>
        留言内容
        <textarea
          name="message"
          placeholder="请说明团队背景、决策场景，以及你希望在未来30到90天达成的目标。"
          required
        ></textarea>
      </label>

      <div class="actions">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">提交信息</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </section>
</Layout>
